article_title: Obamacare Premiums Are On The Rise, But Don't Blame Insurers

article_metadata.author: Capital Flows

og.description: BY LUKE HILGEMANN - The real culprit for higher costs is a federal healthcare law that mandates a one-size-fits-all approach to medicine—and the further we get into its implementation, the worse it gets.
